data.eml:eml: Two new cicada species from Costa Rica (Hemiptera: Cicadomorpha: Cicadidae) with a key to the species of Fidicinoides in Costa Rica

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Sanborn, Allen F., Moore, Thomas E., Young, Allen M. (2008): Two new cicada species from Costa Rica (Hemiptera: Cicadomorpha: Cicadidae) with a key to the species of Fidicinoides in Costa Rica. Zootaxa 1846: 1-20, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.274415
